50|$|Starting in 2010, Michigan International Speedway {{has hosted}} the annual Great Lakes Wine Festival. In 2011, 25 Michigan wineries and 17 breweries {{attended}} this event. The 2011 Great Lakes Wine Festival was a three-day event from Friday, May 20, through Sunday, May 22. The festival offers the opportunity <b>to</b> <b>taste</b> Michigan <b>wine</b> {{from all over}} the state while wineries demonstrate food pairings. MIS has camping available for festival goers to spend the entire weekend.|$|R
